  <body dur="03:07.570">
    <div begin="00:06.720" end="03:07.570">
      <p begin="00:06.720" end="00:09.730" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:06.720" end="00:06.900">Tran</span><span begin="00:06.900" end="00:07.040">s</span><span begin="00:07.040" end="00:07.370">for</span><span begin="00:07.370" end="00:07.660">ming</span> <span begin="00:07.660" end="00:07.710">the</span> <span begin="00:07.850" end="00:08.170">pain</span> <span begin="00:08.210" end="00:08.480">and</span> <span begin="00:08.480" end="00:08.670">re</span><span begin="00:08.670" end="00:08.920">wri</span><span begin="00:08.920" end="00:09.130">ting</span> <span begin="00:09.130" end="00:09.270">your</span> <span begin="00:09.330" end="00:09.730">name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">转化这痛楚 重写你的名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">轉化這痛楚 重寫你的名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">痛みを変換し君の名前を書き換える</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">고통을 변화시키고 너의 이름을 다시 써 내려가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Transformant la douleur et réécrivant ton nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Transformando el dolor y reescribiendo tu nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Schmerz verwandelnd und deinen Namen neu schreibend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Transformando a dor e reescrevendo o seu nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Преобразуя боль и переписывая твое имя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Trasformando il dolore e riscrivendo il tuo nome</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10.260" end="00:13.260" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:10.260" end="00:10.290">「</span><span begin="00:10.290" end="00:10.840">零</span><span begin="00:10.840" end="00:10.870">」</span><span begin="00:10.930" end="00:11.490">戻</span><span begin="00:11.490" end="00:11.680">り</span><span begin="00:11.800" end="00:11.940">ま</span><span begin="00:12.000" end="00:12.070">た</span><span begin="00:12.210" end="00:12.500">再</span><span begin="00:12.600" end="00:13.260">生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">归于零 再次重生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">歸於零 再次重生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning to "zero" and regenerating again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「영」으로 돌아가 다시 재생해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Retournant à « Zéro » et renaissant à nouveau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Regresando a «cero» y reproduciéndome de nuevo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zurück auf "Null" und wiedergeboren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Retornando a «Zero» e regenerando novamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Возвращаюсь к «нулю» и снова перерождаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ritorno allo «zero» e rinasco di nuovo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"Zero" modori mata saisei</span></p>
      <p begin="00:13.440" end="00:15.290" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:13.440" end="00:13.630">I'm</span> <span begin="00:13.630" end="00:13.860">lo</span><span begin="00:13.860" end="00:14.020">st</span> <span begin="00:14.020" end="00:14.280">in</span> <span begin="00:14.280" end="00:14.430">the</span> <span begin="00:14.490" end="00:14.750">hol</span><span begin="00:14.750" end="00:15.170">low</span><span begin="00:15.170" end="00:15.290">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我迷失在无尽的空洞之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我迷失在無盡的空洞之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">虚無の中に迷い込む</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 공허함 속에서 길을 잃었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis perdue dans les abysses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy perdida en los vacíos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bin verloren in der Leere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou perdida nos vazios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я потеряна в пустотах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono persa nei vuoti</span></p>
      <p begin="00:15.240" end="00:18.650" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:15.240" end="00:15.580">運</span><span begin="00:15.580" end="00:15.800">命</span><span begin="00:15.890" end="00:16.400">廻</span><span begin="00:16.400" end="00:16.590">れ</span><span begin="00:16.590" end="00:16.620">、</span><span begin="00:16.920" end="00:17.260">悠</span><span begin="00:17.260" end="00:17.530">久</span><span begin="00:17.560" end="00:17.750">の</span><span begin="00:17.790" end="00:18.030">パ</span><span begin="00:18.030" end="00:18.650">レード</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">命运轮回 悠久的巡游</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">命運輪迴 悠久的巡遊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Fate revolves, an eternal parade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">운명이여 돌아라, 끝없는 행렬이여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que le destin tourne, une parade éternelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Gira el destino, un desfile eterno</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dreh dich Schicksal eine ewige Parade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Gire o destino, um desfile eterno</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вращайся судьба вечный парад</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Gira destino in un'eterna parata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Unmei maware, yuukyuu no pareedo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:18.810" end="00:20.510" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:18.810" end="00:18.940">I</span> <span begin="00:19.030" end="00:19.200">know</span> <span begin="00:19.200" end="00:19.320">the</span> <span begin="00:19.410" end="00:19.560">fate</span> <span begin="00:19.670" end="00:19.890">that</span> <span begin="00:19.890" end="00:20.030">a</span><span begin="00:20.030" end="00:20.330">wai</span><span begin="00:20.330" end="00:20.510">ts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我深知那等待着的宿命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我深知那等待著的宿命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">待ち受ける運命は分かっている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 기다리는 운명을 알고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je connais le destin qui m'attend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Conozco el destino que me espera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kenne das Schicksal das mich erwartet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu conheço o destino que aguarda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я знаю судьбу что ждет впереди</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Conosco il destino che mi attende</span></p>
      <p begin="00:20.260" end="00:23.160" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:20.260" end="00:20.620">Chan</span><span begin="00:20.620" end="00:20.710">ge</span> <span begin="00:20.910" end="00:20.990">me,</span> <span begin="00:21.100" end="00:21.440">for</span><span begin="00:21.440" end="00:21.530">ge</span> <span begin="00:21.730" end="00:21.860">me,</span> <span begin="00:21.950" end="00:22.270">ma</span><span begin="00:22.270" end="00:22.330">ke</span> <span begin="00:22.550" end="00:22.710">me</span> <span begin="00:22.770" end="00:23.160">new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">改变我 锤炼我 让我焕然一新</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">改變我 錘鍊我 讓我煥然一新</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を変えて 鍛え上げて 新しくして</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 변화시키고, 단련하여, 새롭게 만들어 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Change-moi, forge-moi, fais-moi renaître</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cámbiame, fórjame, hazme nueva</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verändere mich schmiede mich mach mich neu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mude-me, forje-me, faça-me nova</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Измени меня перекуй меня сделай меня новой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cambiami forgiami rendimi nuova</span></p>
      <p begin="00:23.590" end="00:25.190" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:23.590" end="00:23.740">Make</span> <span begin="00:23.800" end="00:23.920">me</span> <span begin="00:24.000" end="00:24.110">my</span><span begin="00:24.110" end="00:24.230">th,</span> <span begin="00:24.230" end="00:24.370">ma</span><span begin="00:24.370" end="00:24.420">ke</span> <span begin="00:24.420" end="00:24.540">me</span> <span begin="00:24.600" end="00:24.760">le</span><span begin="00:24.830" end="00:25.190">gend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我化作神话 让我成为传奇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我化作神話 讓我成為傳奇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を神話にして 伝説にして</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 신화로, 전설로 만들어 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais de moi un mythe, fais de moi une légende</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hazme un mito, hazme una leyenda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mach mich zum Mythos mach mich zur Legende</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Faça de mim um mito, faça de mim uma lenda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сделай меня мифом сделай меня легендой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rendimi un mito rendimi una leggenda</span></p>
      <p begin="00:25.230" end="00:26.380" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:25.230" end="00:25.470">Die</span> <span begin="00:25.470" end="00:25.670">and</span> <span begin="00:25.670" end="00:25.890">I</span> <span begin="00:25.890" end="00:25.970">re</span><span begin="00:26.070" end="00:26.380">boot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">死去 然后重启</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">死去 然後重啟</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">死して私は再起動する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">죽고 나서 다시 시작해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je meurs et je redémarre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Muero y me reinicio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sterbe und boote neu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Morro e reinicio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Умираю и перезагружаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Muoio e mi riavvio</span></p>
      <p begin="00:26.880" end="00:29.700" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:26.880" end="00:27.220">E</span><span begin="00:27.220" end="00:27.300">ve</span><span begin="00:27.520" end="00:27.650">ry</span><span begin="00:27.720" end="00:28.040">thing</span> <span begin="00:28.310" end="00:28.540">I</span> <span begin="00:28.540" end="00:28.880">do</span> <span begin="00:29.140" end="00:29.380">for</span> <span begin="00:29.410" end="00:29.700">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我所做的一切皆是为了你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我所做的一切皆是為了你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私の全ては君のために</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 하는 모든 것은 널 위한 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout ce que je fais est pour toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Todo lo que hago por ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles was ich tue tue ich für dich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo o que eu faço é por você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё что я делаю всё ради тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutto ciò che faccio è per te</span></p>
      <p begin="00:29.770" end="00:31.810" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:29.770" end="00:30.000">Go</span> <span begin="00:30.000" end="00:30.220">on</span> <span begin="00:30.220" end="00:30.620">wield</span> <span begin="00:30.620" end="00:30.840">me</span> <span begin="00:30.840" end="00:30.940">li</span><span begin="00:31.000" end="00:31.050">ke</span> <span begin="00:31.050" end="00:31.210">a</span> <span begin="00:31.210" end="00:31.330">wea</span><span begin="00:31.430" end="00:31.810">pon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">来吧 将我如武器般挥舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">來吧 將我如武器般揮舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">さあ私を武器のように振るって</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어서 나를 무기처럼 휘둘러 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vas-y manie-moi comme une arme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Adelante empúñame como un arma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Los führe mich wie eine Waffe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vá em frente me empunhe como uma arma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай же орудуй мной как оружием</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dai impugnami come un'arma</span></p>
      <p begin="00:31.860" end="00:33.040" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:31.860" end="00:31.970">Let</span> <span begin="00:32.040" end="00:32.190">me</span> <span begin="00:32.280" end="00:32.380">meet</span> <span begin="00:32.440" end="00:32.590">my</span> <span begin="00:32.690" end="00:33.040">doom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我迎接我的末日</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我迎接我的末日</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">破滅を迎えさせて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 파멸을 맞이하게 해 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi rencontrer ma perte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame encontrar mi perdición</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich meinem Untergang begegnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixe-me encontrar a minha perdição</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволь мне встретить свою погибель</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lasciami incontrare la mia rovina</span></p>
      <p begin="00:33.520" end="00:36.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:33.520" end="00:34.370">嗚呼</span><span begin="00:34.370" end="00:34.400">、</span><span begin="00:34.740" end="00:34.860">焦</span><span begin="00:34.950" end="00:35.780">が</span><span begin="00:35.780" end="00:35.880">す</span><span begin="00:36.190" end="00:36.270">鼓</span><span begin="00:36.390" end="00:36.690">動</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 焦灼的悸动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 焦灼的悸動</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah, the scorching heartbeat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 애태우는 고동</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah ces battements de cœur qui me consument</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, un latido que arde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah der brennende Herzschlag</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, batida do coração que queima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах это обжигающее биение сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah un battito che brucia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa, kogasu kodou</span></p>
      <p begin="00:36.800" end="00:40.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:36.800" end="00:36.990">繰</span><span begin="00:36.990" end="00:37.060">り</span><span begin="00:37.130" end="00:37.330">返</span><span begin="00:37.330" end="00:37.400">し</span><span begin="00:37.430" end="00:37.530">て</span><span begin="00:37.650" end="00:38.290">も</span><span begin="00:38.290" end="00:38.320">、</span><span begin="00:38.470" end="00:38.710">絶</span><span begin="00:38.780" end="00:39.110">望</span><span begin="00:39.110" end="00:39.230">に</span><span begin="00:39.300" end="00:39.880">抗</span><span begin="00:39.880" end="00:40.010">え</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕无限循环 也要反抗绝望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕無限循環 也要反抗絕望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if it repeats, defy despair</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">반복된다 해도, 절망에 맞서라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je dois répéter, je résisterai au désespoir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque se repita, resiste a la desesperación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn es sich wiederholt leiste der Verzweiflung Widerstand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que se repita, resista ao desespero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже повторяя это вновь и вновь сопротивляйся отчаянию</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se si ripete resisti alla disperazione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kurikaeshite mo, zetsubou ni aragae</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.110" end="00:42.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:40.110" end="00:40.600">Ah,</span> <span begin="00:41.190" end="00:41.460">oh-</span><span begin="00:41.460" end="00:42.810">whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ オオ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 오-워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах о-уоу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah oh-whoa</span></p>
      <p begin="00:43.200" end="00:45.310" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:43.200" end="00:43.760">命</span><span begin="00:43.830" end="00:44.000">か</span><span begin="00:44.050" end="00:44.210">き</span><span begin="00:44.260" end="00:44.460">鳴</span><span begin="00:44.460" end="00:44.560">ら</span><span begin="00:44.650" end="00:44.770">し</span><span begin="00:44.870" end="00:45.310">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">奏响生命的强音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">奏響生命的強音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Strumming my life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">목숨을 튕겨 울리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisant résonner ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Haciendo resonar la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Leben laut aufspielend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fazendo a vida ressoar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заставляя жизнь звучать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Suonando la mia vita a squarciagola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Inochi kakinarashite</span></p>
      <p begin="00:45.700" end="00:49.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:45.700" end="00:45.790">名</span><span begin="00:45.900" end="00:46.100">を</span><span begin="00:46.100" end="00:46.190">失</span><span begin="00:46.280" end="00:46.430">く</span><span begin="00:46.520" end="00:46.640">し</span><span begin="00:46.750" end="00:47.030">て</span><span begin="00:47.170" end="00:47.490">も</span><span begin="00:47.490" end="00:47.520">、</span><span begin="00:47.580" end="00:47.860">僕</span><span begin="00:47.860" end="00:48.010">は</span><span begin="00:48.180" end="00:48.410">在</span><span begin="00:48.410" end="00:48.690">る</span><span begin="00:48.790" end="00:49.150">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕失去名字 我也依然存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕失去名字 我也依然存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I lose my name, saying that I exist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이름을 잃는다 해도, 나는 존재한다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je perds mon nom, j'existe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si pierdo mi nombre, yo existo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn ich meinen Namen verliere existiere ich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu perca meu nome, eu existo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если я потеряю имя я всё равно существую</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se perdo il mio nome io esisto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Na o nakushite mo, boku wa aru to</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.210" end="00:52.120" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:49.210" end="00:49.450">滅</span><span begin="00:49.520" end="00:49.630">び</span><span begin="00:49.850" end="00:49.980">の</span><span begin="00:50.050" end="00:50.730">中</span><span begin="00:50.730" end="00:50.760">、</span><span begin="00:50.860" end="00:51.130">響</span><span begin="00:51.200" end="00:51.510">く</span><span begin="00:51.510" end="00:51.720">ア</span><span begin="00:51.720" end="00:51.940">リ</span><span begin="00:51.940" end="00:52.120">ア</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">毁灭之中 回荡的咏叹调</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">毀滅之中 回盪的詠嘆調</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Amidst ruin, an echoing aria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">멸망 속에서, 울려 퍼지는 아리아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une aria résonnant dans la ruine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En medio de la ruina, resuena un aria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Arie die im Untergang widerhallt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A ária que ressoa em meio à ruína</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Среди разрушения звучит ария</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In mezzo alla distruzione un'aria risuona</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Horobi no naka, hibiku aria</span></p>
      <p begin="00:52.730" end="00:57.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:52.730" end="00:53.160">愛</span><span begin="00:53.180" end="00:53.290">の</span><span begin="00:53.360" end="00:53.690">答</span><span begin="00:53.770" end="00:54.160">え</span> <span begin="00:54.570" end="00:54.700">裂</span><span begin="00:54.790" end="00:56.060">き</span><span begin="00:56.240" end="00:56.720">繋</span><span begin="00:56.720" end="00:56.800">い</span><span begin="00:56.880" end="00:57.430">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">爱的答案 被撕裂又重新相连</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛的答案 被撕裂又重新相連</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The answer of love torn and connected</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑의 대답을 찢어 발기고 이어 붙였어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai déchiré et relié la réponse de l'amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desgarré y uní la respuesta del amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Antwort der Liebe zerrissen und verbunden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A resposta do amor, rasgada e unida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разрывая и связывая ответ любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho strappato e unito la risposta dell'amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai no kotae sakitsunaida</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.090" end="00:58.430" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:57.090" end="00:57.210">Brea</span><span begin="00:57.300" end="00:57.330">k</span> <span begin="00:57.330" end="00:57.430">it,</span> <span begin="00:57.520" end="00:57.730">burn</span> <span begin="00:57.730" end="00:57.810">it,</span> <span begin="00:57.900" end="00:58.110">sa</span><span begin="00:58.110" end="00:58.160">ve</span> <span begin="00:58.160" end="00:58.430">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">打破它 烧毁它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">打破它 燒毀它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">壊して 燃やして 救い出して</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부수고, 불태우고, 구해내</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Brise-le, brûle-le, sauve-le</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Rómpelo, quémalo, sálvalo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrich es verbrenn es rette es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quebre, queime, salve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сломай это сожги это спаси это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rompilo brucialo salvalo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:57.880" end="00:59.530" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="00:57.880" end="00:58.420">囚</span><span begin="00:58.490" end="00:58.790">わ</span><span begin="00:58.930" end="00:59.530">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被囚禁着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被囚禁著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trapped</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얽매인 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Captive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atrapada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gefangen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aprisionada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Плененная</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Prigioniera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Toraware</span></p>
      <p begin="00:59.320" end="00:59.750" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="00:59.320" end="00:59.750">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">耶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">耶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">イェー</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ouais !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Sí!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Да</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Yeah</span></p>
      <p begin="00:59.750" end="01:00.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="00:59.750" end="01:00.010">金</span><span begin="01:00.010" end="01:00.290">輪</span><span begin="01:00.380" end="01:00.780">際</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝不退缩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕不退縮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Never again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">결단코</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À tout jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca más</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Niemals wieder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nunca mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отныне и навсегда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mai più</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Konrinzai</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00.780" end="01:02.960" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:00.780" end="01:00.950">Big</span> <span begin="01:01.080" end="01:01.260">jui</span><span begin="01:01.310" end="01:01.620">cer, and I'm</span> <span begin="01:01.620" end="01:01.850">rea</span><span begin="01:01.850" end="01:01.960">dy</span> <span begin="01:02.020" end="01:02.150">to</span> <span begin="01:02.250" end="01:02.760">cru</span><span begin="01:02.760" end="01:02.960">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">能量拉满 我已准备好粉碎一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">能量拉滿 我已準備好粉碎一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">巨大な力 粉砕する準備はできている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거대한 힘, 전부 짓밟을 준비가 됐어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pleine de puissance et je suis prête à écraser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Gran trituradora, y estoy lista para aplastar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Massive Kraft und ich bin bereit zu zermalmen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com poder total, e estou pronta para esmagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Полная энергии и я готова сокрушать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una forza immensa e sono pronta a distruggere</span></p>
      <p begin="01:03.030" end="01:04.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:03.030" end="01:03.290">もう</span><span begin="01:03.290" end="01:03.530">いい</span><span begin="01:03.670" end="01:04.040">か</span><span begin="01:04.040" end="01:04.170">い</span><span begin="01:04.170" end="01:04.200">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">准备好了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">準備好了嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Are you ready?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이제 된 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Es-tu prête ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Ya estás listo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bist du so weit?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Já está pronta?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты уже готов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei pronto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou ii kai?</span></p>
      <p begin="01:03.980" end="01:06.170" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:03.980" end="01:04.120">S</span><span begin="01:04.120" end="01:04.370">tan</span><span begin="01:04.370" end="01:04.600">ding</span> <span begin="01:04.600" end="01:04.710">in</span> <span begin="01:04.780" end="01:04.860">the</span> <span begin="01:04.950" end="01:05.110">de</span><span begin="01:05.110" end="01:05.190">s</span><span begin="01:05.190" end="01:05.390">tru</span><span begin="01:05.390" end="01:05.450">c</span><span begin="01:05.540" end="01:06.170">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">伫立于毁灭之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">佇立於毀滅之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">破壊の中に立ち</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">파괴의 한가운데 서서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Debout dans la destruction</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">De pie en la destrucción</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Stehe in der Zerstörung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De pé na destruição</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Стоя посреди разрушения</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In piedi nella distruzione</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.930" end="01:07.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:05.930" end="01:06.180">こ</span><span begin="01:06.180" end="01:06.380">の</span><span begin="01:06.380" end="01:06.860">刻</span><span begin="01:07.000" end="01:07.400">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就是这一刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就是這一刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 시간이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Este momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieser Moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Este momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этот самый миг</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questo momento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono toki ga</span></p>
      <p begin="01:07.400" end="01:09.310" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="01:07.400" end="01:07.620">Say</span> <span begin="01:07.620" end="01:07.730">my</span> <span begin="01:07.730" end="01:08.070">name,</span> <span begin="01:08.070" end="01:08.310">we're</span> <span begin="01:08.310" end="01:08.500">en</span><span begin="01:08.500" end="01:08.710">ding</span> <span begin="01:08.710" end="01:08.810">thi</span><span begin="01:08.810" end="01:08.910">s</span> <span begin="01:08.910" end="01:09.310">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呼唤我的名字 就在此刻终结这一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">呼喚我的名字 就在此刻終結這一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私の名前を呼んで 今ここで終わらせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 이름을 불러, 지금 이걸 끝낼 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis mon nom, nous en finissons maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Di mi nombre, estamos terminando esto ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag meinen Namen wir beenden das jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Diga o meu nome, estamos terminando isso agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Назови мое имя мы заканчиваем это прямо сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dì il mio nome stiamo mettendo fine a questo ora</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.270" end="01:09.790" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="01:09.270" end="01:09.460">Wa</span><span begin="01:09.460" end="01:09.580">tch</span> <span begin="01:09.580" end="01:09.790">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看着吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看著吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">見ていて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지켜봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regarde ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Míralo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Pass auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Assista</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотри же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guardalo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.920" end="01:11.350" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="01:09.920" end="01:10.070">You're</span> <span begin="01:10.120" end="01:10.220">gon</span><span begin="01:10.220" end="01:10.290">na</span> <span begin="01:10.340" end="01:10.480">fa</span><span begin="01:10.480" end="01:10.580">ce</span> <span begin="01:10.580" end="01:10.760">my</span> <span begin="01:10.760" end="01:10.980">a</span><span begin="01:10.980" end="01:11.170">ni</span><span begin="01:11.170" end="01:11.350">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你将直面我的灵魂本原</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你將直面我的靈魂本原</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は私の魂と対峙する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너는 내 영혼과 마주하게 될 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu vas faire face à mon anima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Vas a enfrentarte a mi alma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du wirst meiner Anima begegnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você vai enfrentar a minha anima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты столкнешься с моей душой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affronterai la mia anima</span></p>
      <p begin="01:11.580" end="01:13.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="01:11.580" end="01:11.860">Die</span> <span begin="01:11.860" end="01:12.020">and</span> <span begin="01:12.020" end="01:12.200">li</span><span begin="01:12.200" end="01:12.240">ve</span> <span begin="01:12.240" end="01:12.360">it,</span> <span begin="01:12.420" end="01:12.620">now</span> <span begin="01:12.620" end="01:12.820">ge</span><span begin="01:12.820" end="01:12.860">t</span> <span begin="01:12.860" end="01:12.950">up,</span> <span begin="01:13.010" end="01:13.260">ge</span><span begin="01:13.260" end="01:13.290">t</span> <span begin="01:13.290" end="01:13.520">up!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">死去又重生 站起来 站起来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">死去又重生 站起來 站起來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">死して生きろ さあ起き上がれ 起き上がれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">죽고 다시 살아나, 자 일어서, 일어서!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Meurs et vis-le, maintenant lève-toi, lève-toi !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Muere y vívelo, ¡ahora levántate, levántate!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Stirb und lebe es nun steh auf steh auf!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Morra e viva isso, agora levante-se, levante-se!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Умри и проживи это а теперь вставай вставай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Muori e vivilo ora alzati alzati</span></p>
