      <p begin="01:33.480" end="01:36.180" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="01:33.480" end="01:33.900">濁</span><span begin="01:33.930" end="01:34.040">る</span><span begin="01:34.120" end="01:34.220">呼</span><span begin="01:34.310" end="01:34.680">吸</span><span begin="01:34.750" end="01:34.920">の</span><span begin="01:34.920" end="01:35.230">奥</span><span begin="01:35.370" end="01:36.180">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在浑浊的呼吸深处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在渾濁的呼吸深處</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deep within muddy breaths</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">탁해진 호흡 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Au fond d'une respiration trouble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En lo profundo de una respiración turbia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Tief in den trüben Atemzügen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No fundo de uma respiração turva</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В глубине мутного дыхания</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel profondo di un respiro torbido</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nigoru kokyuu no oku de</span></p>
      <p begin="01:36.770" end="01:39.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="01:36.770" end="01:36.990">ひ</span><span begin="01:37.020" end="01:37.160">び</span><span begin="01:37.230" end="01:37.450">割</span><span begin="01:37.450" end="01:37.570">れ</span><span begin="01:37.650" end="01:37.770">た</span><span begin="01:37.830" end="01:38.270">君</span><span begin="01:38.270" end="01:38.360">の</span><span begin="01:38.460" end="01:38.950">影</span> <span begin="01:39.090" end="01:39.560">oh-</span><span begin="01:39.560" end="01:39.940">oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你那布满裂痕的倒影 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你那佈滿裂痕的倒影 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Your cracked shadow oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ひび割れた君の影 オオ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">금이 간 너의 그림자 오-오</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ton ombre fissurée oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tu sombra agrietada oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dein rissiger Schatten oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A sua sombra rachada oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твоя потрескавшаяся тень о-о</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La tua ombra incrinata oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hibiwareta kimi no kage oh-oh</span></p>
      <p begin="01:40.330" end="01:44.190" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="01:40.330" end="01:40.400">無</span><span begin="01:40.510" end="01:40.930">色</span><span begin="01:40.930" end="01:41.100">に</span><span begin="01:41.130" end="01:41.310">な</span><span begin="01:41.340" end="01:41.500">る</span><span begin="01:41.570" end="01:42.110">声</span> <span begin="01:42.410" end="01:43.640">oh-</span><span begin="01:43.640" end="01:44.190">oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渐渐褪去色彩的声音 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漸漸褪去色彩的聲音 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A voice becoming colorless oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">無色になる声 オオ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무색으로 변하는 목소리 오-오</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une voix qui devient incolore oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una voz que se vuelve incolora oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Stimme die farblos wird oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Voz que se torna incolor oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Голос теряющий свои краски о-о</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una voce che diventa incolore oh-oh</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mushoku ni naru koe oh-oh</span></p>
      <p begin="01:44.850" end="01:47.890" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="01:44.850" end="01:45.180">抱</span><span begin="01:45.280" end="01:45.360">き</span><span begin="01:45.490" end="01:45.670">つ</span><span begin="01:45.720" end="01:45.810">づ</span><span begin="01:45.900" end="01:46.060">け</span><span begin="01:46.130" end="01:46.210">た</span> <span begin="01:46.320" end="01:46.450">記</span><span begin="01:46.450" end="01:46.810">憶</span><span begin="01:46.840" end="01:46.980">な</span><span begin="01:47.160" end="01:47.890">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一直紧紧怀抱的 那些记忆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一直緊緊懷抱的 那些記憶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The memories I kept embracing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">계속 품어왔던 기억 따위</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces souvenirs que j'ai continué d'étreindre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los recuerdos que seguí abrazando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Erinnerungen an denen ich immer festhielt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As memórias que continuei abraçando e coisas assim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Воспоминания что я продолжала обнимать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I ricordi che ho continuato ad abbracciare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Idakitsuzuketa kioku nado</span></p>
      <p begin="01:48.400" end="01:49.760" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="01:48.400" end="01:48.550">Re</span><span begin="01:48.600" end="01:48.760">sur</span><span begin="01:48.840" end="01:48.980">rect</span> <span begin="01:49.050" end="01:49.200">whe</span><span begin="01:49.200" end="01:49.260">n</span> <span begin="01:49.260" end="01:49.380">I</span> <span begin="01:49.440" end="01:49.760">die</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">死后复生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">死後復生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">死して復活する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">죽어도 다시 부활해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ressuscite quand je meurs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Resucito cuando muero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auferstehen wenn ich sterbe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ressuscito quando morro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Воскресаю когда умираю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Risorgo quando muoio</span></p>
      <p begin="01:49.820" end="01:51.360" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="01:49.820" end="01:49.960">No</span><span begin="01:50.040" end="01:50.190">thing</span> <span begin="01:50.240" end="01:50.430">to</span> <span begin="01:50.500" end="01:50.620">lo</span><span begin="01:50.620" end="01:50.680">se</span> <span begin="01:50.720" end="01:50.830">whe</span><span begin="01:50.830" end="01:50.910">n</span> <span begin="01:50.910" end="01:50.990">I</span> <span begin="01:51.100" end="01:51.360">fight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">战斗时我一无所惧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">戰鬥時我一無所懼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">戦う時に失うものは何もない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">싸울 때 잃을 것은 아무것도 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rien à perdre quand je combats</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nada que perder cuando peleo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nichts zu verlieren wenn ich kämpfe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nada a perder quando luto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мне нечего терять когда я сражаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Niente da perdere quando combatto</span></p>
      <p begin="01:51.700" end="01:52.990" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="01:51.700" end="01:51.860">I</span> <span begin="01:51.900" end="01:51.990">re</span><span begin="01:51.990" end="01:52.100">s</span><span begin="01:52.140" end="01:52.330">pawn</span> <span begin="01:52.370" end="01:52.560">in</span> <span begin="01:52.560" end="01:52.660">the</span> <span begin="01:52.750" end="01:52.990">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我在黑夜中重生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我在黑夜中重生</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">夜にリスポーンする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어둠 속에서 다시 태어나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je réapparais dans la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Reaparezco en la noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich spawne nachts neu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu renasço na noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я возрождаюсь в ночи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rinasco nella notte</span></p>
