      <p begin="01:54.990" end="01:56.340" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="01:54.990" end="01:55.190">Chan</span><span begin="01:55.190" end="01:55.260">ge</span> <span begin="01:55.260" end="01:55.370">me,</span> <span begin="01:55.450" end="01:55.590">ma</span><span begin="01:55.660" end="01:55.690">ke</span> <span begin="01:55.690" end="01:55.780">me</span> <span begin="01:55.880" end="01:55.980">di</span><span begin="01:56.050" end="01:56.340">vine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">改变我 让我化作神明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">改變我 讓我化作神明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私を変えて 神格化して</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나를 변화시켜, 신성하게 만들어 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Change-moi, rends-moi divine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cámbiame, hazme divina</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verändere mich mach mich göttlich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mude-me, torne-me divina</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Измени меня сделай меня божественной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cambiami rendimi divina</span></p>
