      <p begin="02:03.290" end="02:04.570" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="02:03.290" end="02:03.450">Che</span><span begin="02:03.450" end="02:03.560">ss</span><span begin="02:03.560" end="02:03.770">board,</span> <span begin="02:03.770" end="02:03.920">I</span> <span begin="02:03.920" end="02:04.010">can</span> <span begin="02:04.120" end="02:04.190">p</span><span begin="02:04.190" end="02:04.350">lay</span> <span begin="02:04.350" end="02:04.570">them</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">命运的棋盘 我来运筹帷幄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">命運的棋盤 我來運籌帷幄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">チェスボード 私は操れる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">체스판의 말들, 내가 전부 다뤄주지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur l'échiquier, je peux les jouer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tablero de ajedrez, puedo jugarlos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schachbrett ich kann sie spielen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tabuleiro de xadrez, eu posso jogá-los</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Шахматная доска я могу играть ими</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scacchiera posso giocarci</span></p>
      <p begin="02:04.950" end="02:06.210" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="02:04.950" end="02:05.130">Crea</span><span begin="02:05.170" end="02:05.330">ture</span><span begin="02:05.330" end="02:05.380">s,</span> <span begin="02:05.380" end="02:05.520">I</span> <span begin="02:05.580" end="02:05.660">can</span> <span begin="02:05.710" end="02:05.820">s</span><span begin="02:05.820" end="02:05.990">lay</span> <span begin="02:05.990" end="02:06.210">them</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">邪恶的魔物 我去将之斩杀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">邪惡的魔物 我去將之斬殺</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">魔物たち 私は屠れる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">괴물들, 내가 전부 베어버려 주지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les créatures, je peux les massacrer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Criaturas, puedo matarlas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Kreaturen ich kann sie erschlagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Criaturas, eu posso matá-las</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твари я могу убивать их</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Creature posso ucciderle</span></p>
      <p begin="02:06.580" end="02:07.850" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="02:06.580" end="02:06.720">Brea</span><span begin="02:06.800" end="02:06.830">k</span> <span begin="02:06.830" end="02:06.930">it,</span> <span begin="02:07.010" end="02:07.190">burn</span> <span begin="02:07.230" end="02:07.310">it,</span> <span begin="02:07.420" end="02:07.620">sa</span><span begin="02:07.620" end="02:07.670">ve</span> <span begin="02:07.670" end="02:07.850">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">打破它 烧毁它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">打破它 燒毀它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">壊して 燃やして 救い出して</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부수고, 불태우고, 구해내</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Brise-le, brûle-le, sauve-le</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Rómpelo, quémalo, sálvalo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrich es verbrenn es rette es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quebre, queime, salve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сломай это сожги это спаси это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rompilo brucialo salvalo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:07.850" end="02:10.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="02:07.850" end="02:08.300">Ah,</span> <span begin="02:08.920" end="02:09.930">oh-</span><span begin="02:09.930" end="02:10.350">whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ オオ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 오-워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах о-уоу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah oh-whoa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:08.280" end="02:09.570" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="02:08.280" end="02:08.410">Wa</span><span begin="02:08.470" end="02:08.590">king</span> <span begin="02:08.660" end="02:08.830">some</span><span begin="02:08.890" end="02:09.000">thing</span> <span begin="02:09.100" end="02:09.240">an</span><span begin="02:09.310" end="02:09.570">cient</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唤醒某些古老的存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喚醒某些古老的存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">古代の何かを目覚めさせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">태고의 무언가를 깨워내며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Réveillant quelque chose d'ancien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Despertando algo antiguo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Etwas Uraltes erweckend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Despertando algo antigo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пробуждая нечто древнее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Risvegliando qualcosa di antico</span></p>
      <p begin="02:09.750" end="02:11.200" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L54"><span begin="02:09.750" end="02:09.820">Ma</span><span begin="02:09.930" end="02:09.980">ke</span> <span begin="02:09.980" end="02:10.140">the</span> <span begin="02:10.140" end="02:10.370">whole</span> <span begin="02:10.370" end="02:10.530">world</span> <span begin="02:10.580" end="02:10.710">my</span> <span begin="02:10.790" end="02:10.990">play</span><span begin="02:10.990" end="02:11.200">pen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让整个世界化作我的游乐场</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓整個世界化作我的遊樂場</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">全世界を私の遊び場にする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">온 세상을 내 놀이터로 만들어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisant du monde entier mon terrain de jeu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hago del mundo entero mi área de juegos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mache die ganze Welt zu meinem Spielplatz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fazer do mundo inteiro o meu cercadinho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сделаю весь мир своим манежем для игр</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Faccio del mondo intero il mio recinto di gioco</span></p>
      <p begin="02:10.880" end="02:13.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L55"><span begin="02:10.880" end="02:11.480">命</span><span begin="02:11.560" end="02:11.720">か</span><span begin="02:11.780" end="02:11.920">き</span><span begin="02:11.990" end="02:12.170">鳴</span><span begin="02:12.170" end="02:12.290">ら</span><span begin="02:12.360" end="02:12.490">し</span><span begin="02:12.580" end="02:13.000">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">奏响生命的强音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">奏響生命的強音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Strumming my life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">목숨을 튕겨 울리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisant résonner ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Haciendo resonar la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein Leben laut aufspielend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fazendo a vida ressoar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заставляя жизнь звучать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Suonando la mia vita a squarciagola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Inochi kakinarashite</span></p>
      <p begin="02:13.440" end="02:16.890" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L56"><span begin="02:13.440" end="02:13.860">全</span><span begin="02:13.860" end="02:13.970">部</span><span begin="02:14.050" end="02:14.300">消</span><span begin="02:14.300" end="02:14.390">え</span><span begin="02:14.500" end="02:14.720">て</span><span begin="02:14.890" end="02:15.180">も</span><span begin="02:15.180" end="02:15.210">、</span><span begin="02:15.310" end="02:15.430">こ</span><span begin="02:15.480" end="02:15.610">こ</span><span begin="02:15.640" end="02:15.780">に</span><span begin="02:15.960" end="02:16.170">い</span><span begin="02:16.170" end="02:16.540">る</span><span begin="02:16.540" end="02:16.890">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕一切消散 我也依然在这里哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕一切消散 我也依然在這裡哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if everything disappears, I am right here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">전부 사라진다 해도, 여기에 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si tout disparaît, je suis là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si todo desaparece, estoy aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn alles verschwindet bin ich hier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que tudo desapareça, eu estou aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если всё исчезнет я буду здесь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se tutto dovesse scomparire io sono qui</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zenbu kiete mo, koko ni iru yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:16.980" end="02:20.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L57"><span begin="02:16.980" end="02:17.250">祈</span><span begin="02:17.250" end="02:17.440">り</span><span begin="02:17.600" end="02:17.710">の</span><span begin="02:17.820" end="02:18.470">中</span><span begin="02:18.470" end="02:18.500">、</span><span begin="02:18.610" end="02:18.920">巡</span><span begin="02:18.920" end="02:19.190">る</span><span begin="02:19.230" end="02:19.430">カ</span><span begin="02:19.430" end="02:19.630">ル</span><span begin="02:19.660" end="02:20.140">マ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">祈祷之中 轮回的业果</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">祈禱之中 輪迴的業果</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Karma circling within prayers</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기도 속에서, 맴도는 업보</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le karma tournoyant dans la prière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En medio de la oración, el karma que da vueltas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Karma das im Gebet kreist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em meio à oração, o carma que circula</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Внутри молитвы круговорот кармы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il karma che gira in mezzo alle preghiere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Inori no naka, meguru karuma</span></p>
      <p begin="02:20.460" end="02:25.120" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L58"><span begin="02:20.460" end="02:20.870">重</span><span begin="02:20.910" end="02:21.060">ね</span><span begin="02:21.090" end="02:21.300">合</span><span begin="02:21.300" end="02:21.400">わ</span><span begin="02:21.510" end="02:21.960">せ</span> <span begin="02:22.340" end="02:23.760">愛</span><span begin="02:23.960" end="02:24.200">し</span><span begin="02:24.230" end="02:24.450">た</span><span begin="02:24.450" end="02:24.630">ん</span><span begin="02:24.630" end="02:25.120">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将其层层交叠 深深爱着啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將其層層交疊 深深愛著啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Overlapping them I loved you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">겹쳐 포개며 사랑한 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En les superposant, je les ai aimés</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Superponiéndolos los amé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schicht für Schicht habe ich dich geliebt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sobrepondo-os, eu amei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Накладывая друг на друга я любила это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si sono sovrapposti e ho amato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kasaneawase aishitan da</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.810" end="02:26.080" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L59"><span begin="02:24.810" end="02:24.940">Brea</span><span begin="02:25.020" end="02:25.050">k</span> <span begin="02:25.050" end="02:25.180">it,</span> <span begin="02:25.240" end="02:25.410">burn</span> <span begin="02:25.450" end="02:25.540">it,</span> <span begin="02:25.640" end="02:25.840">sa</span><span begin="02:25.840" end="02:25.900">ve</span> <span begin="02:25.900" end="02:26.080">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">打破它 烧毁它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">打破它 燒毀它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">壊して 燃やして 救い出して</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부수고, 불태우고, 구해내</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Brise-le, brûle-le, sauve-le</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Rómpelo, quémalo, sálvalo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrich es verbrenn es rette es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quebre, queime, salve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сломай это сожги это спаси это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rompilo brucialo salvalo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:26.660" end="02:30.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L60"><span begin="02:26.660" end="02:26.780">名</span><span begin="02:26.870" end="02:27.080">を</span><span begin="02:27.080" end="02:27.180">失</span><span begin="02:27.250" end="02:27.410">く</span><span begin="02:27.480" end="02:27.630">し</span><span begin="02:27.710" end="02:27.990">て</span><span begin="02:28.140" end="02:28.440">も</span><span begin="02:28.440" end="02:28.470">、</span><span begin="02:28.530" end="02:28.840">僕</span><span begin="02:28.840" end="02:28.970">は</span><span begin="02:29.180" end="02:29.380">在</span><span begin="02:29.380" end="02:29.630">る</span><span begin="02:29.760" end="02:30.100">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕失去名字 我也依然存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕失去名字 我也依然存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I lose my name, saying that I exist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이름을 잃는다 해도, 나는 존재한다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je perds mon nom, j'existe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si pierdo mi nombre, yo existo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn ich meinen Namen verliere existiere ich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu perca meu nome, eu existo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если я потеряю имя я всё равно существую</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se perdo il mio nome io esisto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Na o nakushite mo, boku wa aru to</span></p>
      <p begin="02:30.150" end="02:33.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L61"><span begin="02:30.150" end="02:30.410">滅</span><span begin="02:30.480" end="02:30.610">び</span><span begin="02:30.800" end="02:31.000">の</span><span begin="02:31.000" end="02:31.700">中</span><span begin="02:31.700" end="02:31.730">、</span><span begin="02:31.830" end="02:32.080">響</span><span begin="02:32.150" end="02:32.450">く</span><span begin="02:32.450" end="02:32.680">ア</span><span begin="02:32.680" end="02:32.920">リ</span><span begin="02:32.920" end="02:33.110">ア</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">毁灭之中 回荡的咏叹调</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">毀滅之中 回盪的詠嘆調</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Amidst ruin, an echoing aria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">멸망 속에서, 울려 퍼지는 아리아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une aria résonnant dans la ruine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En medio de la ruina, resuena un aria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Arie die im Untergang widerhallt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A ária que ressoa em meio à ruína</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Среди разрушения звучит ария</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In mezzo alla distruzione un'aria risuona</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Horobi no naka, hibiku aria</span></p>
      <p begin="02:33.740" end="02:38.370" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L62"><span begin="02:33.740" end="02:34.140">愛</span><span begin="02:34.140" end="02:34.260">の</span><span begin="02:34.340" end="02:34.650">答</span><span begin="02:34.740" end="02:35.120">え</span> <span begin="02:35.550" end="02:35.680">裂</span><span begin="02:35.760" end="02:37.010">き</span><span begin="02:37.200" end="02:37.690">繋</span><span begin="02:37.690" end="02:37.760">い</span><span begin="02:37.840" end="02:38.370">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">爱的答案 被撕裂又重新相连</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛的答案 被撕裂又重新相連</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The answer of love torn and connected</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑의 대답을 찢어 발기고 이어 붙였어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai déchiré et relié la réponse de l'amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desgarré y uní la respuesta del amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Antwort der Liebe zerrissen und verbunden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A resposta do amor, rasgada e unida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разрывая и связывая ответ любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho strappato e unito la risposta dell'amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai no kotae sakitsunaida</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.050" end="02:39.400" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L63"><span begin="02:38.050" end="02:38.160">Brea</span><span begin="02:38.260" end="02:38.300">k</span> <span begin="02:38.300" end="02:38.400">it,</span> <span begin="02:38.480" end="02:38.680">burn</span> <span begin="02:38.710" end="02:38.780">it,</span> <span begin="02:38.860" end="02:39.080">sa</span><span begin="02:39.080" end="02:39.140">ve</span> <span begin="02:39.140" end="02:39.400">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">打破它 烧毁它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">打破它 燒毀它 拯救它</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">壊して 燃やして 救い出して</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부수고, 불태우고, 구해내</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Brise-le, brûle-le, sauve-le</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Rómpelo, quémalo, sálvalo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrich es verbrenn es rette es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quebre, queime, salve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сломай это сожги это спаси это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rompilo brucialo salvalo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.860" end="02:40.510" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L64"><span begin="02:38.860" end="02:39.390">囚</span><span begin="02:39.440" end="02:39.760">わ</span><span begin="02:39.880" end="02:40.510">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被囚禁着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被囚禁著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trapped</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얽매인 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Captive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atrapada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gefangen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aprisionada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Плененная</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Prigioniera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Toraware</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.300" end="02:40.690" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L65"><span begin="02:40.300" end="02:40.690">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">耶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">耶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">イェー</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ouais !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Sí!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Yeah!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Да</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Yeah</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.700" end="02:41.750" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L66"><span begin="02:40.700" end="02:40.980">金</span><span begin="02:40.980" end="02:41.240">輪</span><span begin="02:41.340" end="02:41.750">際</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝不退缩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕不退縮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Never again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">결단코</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À tout jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca más</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Niemals wieder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nunca mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Отныне и навсегда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mai più</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Konrinzai</span></p>
      <p begin="02:41.750" end="02:43.880" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L67"><span begin="02:41.750" end="02:41.910">Big</span> <span begin="02:42.030" end="02:42.210">jui</span><span begin="02:42.260" end="02:42.590">cer, and I'm</span> <span begin="02:42.590" end="02:42.830">rea</span><span begin="02:42.830" end="02:42.890">dy</span> <span begin="02:43.000" end="02:43.120">to</span> <span begin="02:43.210" end="02:43.720">cru</span><span begin="02:43.720" end="02:43.880">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">能量拉满 我已准备好粉碎一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">能量拉滿 我已準備好粉碎一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">巨大な力 粉砕する準備はできている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거대한 힘, 전부 짓밟을 준비가 됐어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pleine de puissance et je suis prête à écraser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Gran trituradora, y estoy lista para aplastar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Massive Kraft und ich bin bereit zu zermalmen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com poder total, e estou pronta para esmagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Полная энергии и я готова сокрушать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una forza immensa e sono pronta a distruggere</span></p>
      <p begin="02:44.000" end="02:45.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L68"><span begin="02:44.000" end="02:44.250">もう</span><span begin="02:44.250" end="02:44.490">いい</span><span begin="02:44.610" end="02:44.990">か</span><span begin="02:44.990" end="02:45.110">い</span><span begin="02:45.110" end="02:45.140">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">准备好了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">準備好了嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Are you ready?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이제 된 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Es-tu prête ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Ya estás listo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bist du so weit?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Já está pronta?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты уже готов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei pronto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou ii kai?</span></p>
      <p begin="02:44.950" end="02:47.160" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L69"><span begin="02:44.950" end="02:45.090">S</span><span begin="02:45.090" end="02:45.330">tan</span><span begin="02:45.330" end="02:45.560">ding</span> <span begin="02:45.560" end="02:45.720">in</span> <span begin="02:45.720" end="02:45.850">the</span> <span begin="02:45.920" end="02:46.060">de</span><span begin="02:46.060" end="02:46.160">s</span><span begin="02:46.160" end="02:46.360">tru</span><span begin="02:46.360" end="02:46.410">c</span><span begin="02:46.510" end="02:47.160">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">伫立于毁灭之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">佇立於毀滅之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">破壊の中に立ち</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">파괴의 한가운데 서서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Debout dans la destruction</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">De pie en la destrucción</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Stehe in der Zerstörung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De pé na destruição</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Стоя посреди разрушения</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In piedi nella distruzione</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.900" end="02:48.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L70"><span begin="02:46.900" end="02:47.150">こ</span><span begin="02:47.150" end="02:47.310">の</span><span begin="02:47.350" end="02:47.810">刻</span><span begin="02:47.970" end="02:48.400">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就是这一刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就是這一刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 시간이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Este momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieser Moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Este momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этот самый миг</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questo momento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono toki ga</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.350" end="02:50.290" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L71"><span begin="02:48.350" end="02:48.590">Say</span> <span begin="02:48.590" end="02:48.720">my</span> <span begin="02:48.720" end="02:49.040">name,</span> <span begin="02:49.040" end="02:49.280">we're</span> <span begin="02:49.280" end="02:49.470">en</span><span begin="02:49.470" end="02:49.660">ding</span> <span begin="02:49.660" end="02:49.770">thi</span><span begin="02:49.770" end="02:49.880">s</span> <span begin="02:49.880" end="02:50.290">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呼唤我的名字 就在此刻终结这一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">呼喚我的名字 就在此刻終結這一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私の名前を呼んで 今ここで終わらせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 이름을 불러, 지금 이걸 끝낼 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis mon nom, nous en finissons maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Di mi nombre, estamos terminando esto ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag meinen Namen wir beenden das jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Diga o meu nome, estamos terminando isso agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Назови мое имя мы заканчиваем это прямо сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dì il mio nome stiamo mettendo fine a questo ora</span></p>
      <p begin="02:50.240" end="02:50.770" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L72"><span begin="02:50.240" end="02:50.430">Wa</span><span begin="02:50.430" end="02:50.530">tch</span> <span begin="02:50.530" end="02:50.770">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看着吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看著吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">見ていて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지켜봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regarde ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Míralo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Pass auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Assista</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотри же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guardalo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:50.880" end="02:52.400" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L73"><span begin="02:50.880" end="02:51.020">you're</span> <span begin="02:51.080" end="02:51.170">gon</span><span begin="02:51.170" end="02:51.270">na</span> <span begin="02:51.310" end="02:51.450">fa</span><span begin="02:51.450" end="02:51.540">ce</span> <span begin="02:51.540" end="02:51.730">my</span> <span begin="02:51.730" end="02:51.950">a</span><span begin="02:51.950" end="02:52.160">ni</span><span begin="02:52.160" end="02:52.400">ma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你将直面我的灵魂本原</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你將直面我的靈魂本原</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は私の魂と対峙する</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너는 내 영혼과 마주하게 될 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu vas faire face à mon anima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">vas a enfrentarte a mi alma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du wirst meiner Anima begegnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você vai enfrentar a minha anima</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты столкнешься с моей душой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affronterai la mia anima</span></p>
      <p begin="02:52.530" end="02:54.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L74"><span begin="02:52.530" end="02:52.760">Die</span> <span begin="02:52.760" end="02:52.980">and</span> <span begin="02:52.980" end="02:53.140">li</span><span begin="02:53.140" end="02:53.190">ve</span> <span begin="02:53.190" end="02:53.290">it,</span> <span begin="02:53.350" end="02:53.580">now</span> <span begin="02:53.580" end="02:53.780">ge</span><span begin="02:53.780" end="02:53.820">t</span> <span begin="02:53.820" end="02:53.930">up,</span> <span begin="02:53.980" end="02:54.220">ge</span><span begin="02:54.220" end="02:54.250">t</span> <span begin="02:54.250" end="02:54.460">up!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">死去又重生 站起来 站起来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">死去又重生 站起來 站起來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">死して生きろ さあ起き上がれ 起き上がれ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">죽고 다시 살아나, 자 일어서, 일어서!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Meurs et vis-le, maintenant lève-toi, lève-toi !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Muere y vívelo, ¡ahora levántate, levántate!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Stirb und lebe es nun steh auf steh auf!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Morra e viva isso, agora levante-se, levante-se!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Умри и проживи это а теперь вставай вставай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Muori e vivilo ora alzati alzati</span></p>
      <p begin="02:54.900" end="02:58.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L75"><span begin="02:54.900" end="02:55.570">Whoa!</span> <span begin="02:56.410" end="02:57.410">Oh-</span><span begin="02:57.410" end="02:57.610">wh</span><span begin="02:57.610" end="02:58.260">o</span><span begin="02:58.260" end="02:58.330">a</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喔 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喔 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ウォー オオ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">워! 오-워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Whoa ! Oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Whoa! Oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Whoa! Oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Whoa! Oh-whoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Уоу о-уоу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Whoa oh-whoa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:59.520" end="03:00.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L76"><span begin="02:59.520" end="02:59.790">Yo,</span> <span begin="02:59.930" end="03:00.090">che</span><span begin="03:00.140" end="03:00.190">ck</span> <span begin="03:00.190" end="03:00.250">it</span> <span begin="03:00.250" end="03:00.720">out!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哟 仔细看好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喲 仔細看好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ヨォ 見てな</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">자, 똑똑히 봐!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Yo, regarde ça !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye, ¡mira esto!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Yo sieh dir das an!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Yo, saca só!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Йо зацени</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Yo dai un'occhiata</span></p>
      <p begin="03:01.030" end="03:04.070" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L77"><span begin="03:01.030" end="03:01.170">残</span><span begin="03:01.220" end="03:01.440">響</span><span begin="03:01.440" end="03:01.550">か</span><span begin="03:01.550" end="03:01.640">ら</span><span begin="03:01.640" end="03:01.770">乱</span><span begin="03:01.870" end="03:02.280">深</span><span begin="03:02.280" end="03:02.450">化</span> <span begin="03:02.690" end="03:03.030">結</span><span begin="03:03.030" end="03:03.100">ん</span><span begin="03:03.100" end="03:03.240">でい</span><span begin="03:03.290" end="03:03.400">た</span><span begin="03:03.490" end="03:03.900">因</span><span begin="03:03.900" end="03:04.070">果</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">残响之中深化错乱 曾紧密相连的因果</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殘響之中深化錯亂 曾緊密相連的因果</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Chaotic deepening from the reverberation the causality that was tied</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잔향에서 깊어지는 혼란, 맺어져 있던 인과</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une évolution chaotique depuis la réverbération, le karma que nous avions lié</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Profundización caótica desde la reverberación la causa y efecto que nos unía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aus dem Nachhall vertieft sich das Chaos das verbundene Karma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aprofundamento caótico da reverberação, o carma que estava ligado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хаотичное углубление из отголосков связанная карма</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dal riverbero un caos più profondo il karma che ci legava</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zankyou kara ranshinka musunde ita inga</span></p>
      <p begin="03:04.330" end="03:07.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L78"><span begin="03:04.330" end="03:04.460">隠</span><span begin="03:04.520" end="03:04.640">さ</span><span begin="03:04.640" end="03:04.690">れ</span><span begin="03:04.740" end="03:04.850">た</span><span begin="03:04.930" end="03:05.190">ア</span><span begin="03:05.190" end="03:05.270">ル</span><span begin="03:05.350" end="03:05.580">カ</span><span begin="03:05.580" end="03:05.670">ナ</span> <span begin="03:05.740" end="03:06.180">さあ</span><span begin="03:06.180" end="03:06.210">、</span><span begin="03:06.220" end="03:06.340">Re</span><span begin="03:06.400" end="03:06.610">col</span><span begin="03:06.650" end="03:06.830">lect</span> <span begin="03:06.990" end="03:07.570">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被隐秘的阿尔卡纳 来吧 此刻尽数回想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被隱秘的阿爾卡納 來吧 此刻盡數回想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The hidden arcana come on, Recollect now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">隠されたアルカナ さあ 今すぐ記憶を呼び覚まして</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">숨겨진 아르카나 자, 지금 다시 떠올려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les arcanes cachés, allez, souviens-toi maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los arcanos ocultos vamos, recuérdalo ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verborgene Arkana nun erinnere dich jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Arcana oculta vamos lá, relembre agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скрытая аркана ну же вспомни теперь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Arcani nascosti ora ricorda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakusareta arukana saa, recollect now</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
